eline N failing {…} → now M: {…}`. | Prioritize when: never re-renders, a screenshot of the wrong screen, a fixture older than your work making a green result suspect. \\\"No r…\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"triggered\": [\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 6626,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/007-system-spec-kit-rename\",\n          \"title\": \"Skill Rename [system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/007-system-spec-kit-rename/spec]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"skill\",\n            \"workflows\",\n            \"spec\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 8624,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/024-compact-code-graph/015-tree-sitter-migration\",\n          \"title\": \"Spec: Tree-Sitter WASM Migration [024/015] [system-spec-kit/024-compact-code-graph/015-tree-sitter-migration/spec]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"spec\",\n            \"015\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 8109,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/022-hybrid-rag-fusion/013-agents-alignment\",\n          \"title\": \"013 — Agent Alignment: Runtime Lineage Truth [system-spec-kit/022-hybrid-rag-fusion/013-agents-alignment/spec]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"lineage\",\n            \"spec\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 7600,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/022-hybrid-rag-fusion/006-feature-catalog\",\n          \"title\": \"Feature Catalog Comprehensive Audit & Remediation [system-spec-kit/022-hybrid-rag-fusion/006-feature-catalog/spec]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"remediation\",\n            \"spec\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 7282,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/013-memory-overhaul-and-agent-upgrade-release/002-skill-speck