 last two new-findings ratios are `0.08 -> 0.00`, but convergence is telemetry only because `stopPolicy=max-iterations`. The loop legally stops because iteration 5 reached `config.maxIterations`.\n+\n+## Final Iteration Verdict\n+\n+This iteration itself has no new P0/P1 findings, so the per-iteration verdict is PASS. The synthesis verdict remains CONDITIONAL because active P1 findings remain open.\n+\n+Review verdict: PASS\n\nIndex: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/015-skill-doc-drift-remediation/review/lineages/gpt-fast-high/deltas/iteration-001.json\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/015-skill-doc-drift-remediation/review/lineages/gpt-fast-high/deltas/iteration-001.json\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/015-skill-doc-drift-remediation/review/lineages/gpt-fast-high/deltas/iteration-001.json\n@@ -0,0 +1,10 @@\n+{\n+  \"type\": \"iteration_delta\",\n+  \"iteration\": 1,\n+  \"dimension\": \"correctness\",\n+  \"findingsNew\": 1,\n+  \"newFindingsRatio\": 0.5,\n+  \"findingsSummary\": { \"P0\": 0, \"P1\": 1, \"P2\": 0 },\n+  \"findingRefs\": [\"F001\"],\n+  \"verdict\": \"CONDITIONAL\"\n+}\n\nIndex: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/015-skill-doc-drift-remediation/review/lineages/gpt-fast-high/deltas/iteration-002.json\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/015-skill-doc-drift-remediation/review/lineages/gpt-fast-high/deltas/iteration-002.js