oc-drift-remediation/review/lineages/gpt-fast-high/prompts/iteration-003.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/015-skill-doc-drift-remediation/review/lineages/gpt-fast-high/prompts/iteration-003.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,1 @@\n+STATE SUMMARY: Iteration 3 of 5. Focus traceability. Compare spec, plan, tasks, checklist, implementation summary, and graph metadata. Write output to iterations/iteration-003.md. Do not modify target files.\n\nIndex: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/015-skill-doc-drift-remediation/review/lineages/gpt-fast-high/prompts/iteration-004.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/015-skill-doc-drift-remediation/review/lineages/gpt-fast-high/prompts/iteration-004.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/015-skill-doc-drift-remediation/review/lineages/gpt-fast-high/prompts/iteration-004.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,1 @@\n+STATE SUMMARY: Iteration 4 of 5. Focus maintainability. Check metadata coverage and discoverability after expanded remediation scope. Write output to iterations/iteration-004.md. Do not modify target files.\n\nIndex: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/015-skill-doc-drift-remediation/review/lineages/gpt-fast-high/prompts/iteration-005.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/031-deep-loop-issues-with-gpt-opencode/015-skill-doc-drift-remediation/review/lineages/gpt-fast-high/prom